data.title: Ingles Basico 1° Parcial 14-04-22
data.meta_description: INGLES BASICO 1° PARCIAL 14-04-22 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document contains an English vocabulary exercise with multiple choice questions, fill-in-the-blank exercises, and matching exercises. It tests basic English skills like matching sentence halves, choosing the correct answers to questions, completing sentences, and matching questions to answers. The exercises cover topics like seasons, locations, occupations, schedules, and personal details to gauge a student's fundamental English comprehension.
